    "description": "《<strong>ASCENXION : 降临</strong>》是一款是探险通关的2D射击动作游戏。采用了通过探险获得的能力和道具解锁新区域的，银河恶魔城风格类型游戏的进行方式。<br><br>玩家需在场景中突破战斗和拼图，舰艇，精英小组，并且BOSS战斗等多种障碍物，通过以此来获得的奖励逐渐强大，并了解世界的真相。<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >摘要</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/cb7319fa30402aadb893c55742797381.poster.avif?t=1727464289\" width=640 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/cb7319fa30402aadb893c55742797381.webm?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/cb7319fa30402aadb893c55742797381.mp4?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>有一天，人类随着巨大的爆炸灭亡了。包括传承灭亡理由的人，悼念已灭亡的人而记住他们的人，任何人都没有存活下来。<br><br>之后流逝了漫长的岁月，在人类文明痕迹中，你已苏醒。漫无边际地飘荡的你，会遇到人类留下的各种记录和帮助你的存在。你能找出这个世界的秘密，并且面对真相吗？<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><strong>战略性快节奏战斗</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/5e6159d13c1035267147ed15cfc24a8b.poster.avif?t=1727464289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/5e6159d13c1035267147ed15cfc24a8b.webm?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/5e6159d13c1035267147ed15cfc24a8b.mp4?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《ASCENXION : 降临》虽然是射击动作游戏，但为了提供与其他弹幕射击游戏不同的战斗经验，没有设计成躲避敌人的弹幕进行攻击，而设计成着重作用选择和集中。<br><br>准备了活用地形的掩蔽，普通攻击时减少的移动速度，攻击技能和躲避技能消耗的资源的相互共享等多种战略要素，玩家要适当地使用普通攻击和技能，以及道具的主动效果等来击退敌人。<br><br><br><strong>通过探险可获得的道具</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/f3c73bbed8a20e6055b4df520dda3e22.poster.avif?t=1727464289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/f3c73bbed8a20e6055b4df520dda3e22.webm?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/f3c73bbed8a20e6055b4df520dda3e22.mp4?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩家可在未知的土地上探险，并获得数十种特色道具。道具分为和武器共享使用效果的“符文石”，还有赋予基本持续效果及能力值加成的普通道具。<br><br><br><strong>成长体系</strong><br>《ASCENXION : 降临》中存在“潜力开放”和“技能”的概念。每个机体拥有4个技能，从第二个技能开始，在击退游戏BOSS怪时可解锁。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>技能</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/da5d86b160d3bdbdd7b898597ef30c36.poster.avif?t=1727464289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/da5d86b160d3bdbdd7b898597ef30c36.webm?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/da5d86b160d3bdbdd7b898597ef30c36.mp4?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>各阶段的技能只能二选一，但随时可以改变选择。需要根据周边地形和敌人类型等实际情况变更技能的判断力！<br><br></li><li><strong>潜力开放</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/dfbe4e79ffc3d75adc0867e83c1061d4.poster.avif?t=1727464289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/dfbe4e79ffc3d75adc0867e83c1061d4.webm?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000000/extras/dfbe4e79ffc3d75adc0867e83c1061d4.mp4?t=1727464289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《ASCENXION : 降临》的主人公是内心中封印着强大力量的角色。当然，强大的力量是可以解放的。在游戏进行过程中，完成必然碰到的活动，即可开放力量，力量开放后，所有技能和整体能力值都将按照开放的机体概念进行变更。开放的机体具有不同的战斗风格，请挑选自己喜欢的并成长吧！</li></ul>",
